Author: BitsOfAByte
Name: Kiko Guide
Punchline: The ultimate collections of guides for any in-game content! Dungeons, Trials, Raids, FATEs and more supported!
Description:
Comprehensive guides for any in-game content, powered by a strong custom guide system with the ability to add your own notes. Never forget the mechanics while in a duty roulette again!

All guides are written by project contributors - please see the GitHub repository for more information on how to contribute your own content or help translate existing content.
